OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRain slowly moving across
OL,6,Fnorthern Scotland. Elsewhere, an
OL,7,Fovercast and murky start, with showers
OL,8,Faffecting the southwest. Turning a
OL,9,Flittle brighter with sunny spells
OL,10,Fdeveloping. Further showers are likely
OL,11,Fto break out during the day across
OL,12,Fsouthern England and Wales.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FShowers across the south
OL,15,Fmostly fading during the evening.
OL,16,FOtherwise dry, with variable amounts
OL,17,Fof cloud. Cloudier in the north, with
OL,18,Fpatchy rain sinking south across parts
OL,19,Fof Scotland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
