OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FDry for many, with variable
OL,6,Famounts of cloud and sunny spells.
OL,7,FShowery outbreaks of rain continuing
OL,8,Fto push south across northern areas.
OL,9,FBrighter conditions follow as colder
OL,10,Fair arrives.
